                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 823.00/104.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                            <gloss type="to">American Minister</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1913-07-29">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 29, 1913</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Use whatever influence you properly can to protect the life of ex-President
                    Leguía. Say to the President that our deep interest in the welfare of Peru leads
                    us to express the hope that any differences which may have arisen in that
                    country will be settled by peaceful means and legal processes.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Bryan</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
